{"tid":235463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：活化工廈政策成功","createTime":"2017-05-09T04:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T04:52:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cf7ff44b34c3471732f28132d4c3469f1c4351","tid":235463,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官梁振英將率團到北京出席一帶一路高峰論壇，候任特首林鄭月娥是否隨團是由中央決定，他又強調這次論壇香港獲高規格安排。<br />\n<br />\n被問觀塘一座工廈的表演場地有外籍樂隊涉嫌從事非法勞工被捕，梁振英表示，是考慮到觀眾及大廈使用者安全，而外地表演者亦需要有工作簽證，強調活化工廈政策是成功。"},{"pid":"283a769f7e07c41bc0a83ff0a5889947c634351e","tid":235463,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=220460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220460&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f8158e56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220460&h=f8d452ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=220460</a>"},{"pid":"d01d9ed45077e2a4e94c2dd54650a6b32d3b4e5e","tid":235463,"uid":1265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"之前有台妹黎香港私影都拉左坐監<br />\n好合理"},{"pid":"3f601dd1ee86204f04898d2671235919c920ad8b","tid":235463,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:48:47.000Z","msg":"前晚Hidden Agenda邀請英國樂隊表演，樂隊因未有申請工作簽證遭入境處拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英今早出席行政會議前被問到事件，是否反映活化工廈政策不成功，梁稱政策屬成功，但與工廈有關的政策必須考慮使用大廈人士的安全，包括樂隊及觀眾等，「唔係喺工廈做咩都可以」，故在活化工廈時，曾有取締工廈非法活動的行動。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調入境政策下，任何人士來港工作都需要工作簽證。"},{"pid":"219798531ef59aff7f93ffc158e35302454f8781","tid":235463,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"支持梁特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874c38b1678120ae748fc290ea9618486c7130cd","tid":235463,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"咁活化完個用途完全無變，條例甚至更加捉得緊<br />\n咁究竟活化左啲乜鳩...耐人尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}